  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Upper gastrointestinal system endoscopy is widely used for diagnostic approach. To increase
      the tolerability and compliance of the patient, sedation is applied. There are many studies
      showing that sedation increases the patient compliance and the tolerability. However,
      spasmolytic use in GE has not been evaluated yet.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
