  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  no hypersensitivity to the agent.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Emergent cases,the cases with low mental compatibility and pregnant women were
             excluded from the study. Moreover, the procedures under sedation, cases with disorders
             decreasing the intestinal motility like hypothyroidism and diabetes were excluded.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
